    "text": "Fooducate\nlogin / signup\nBROWSE\nCOMMUNITY\nRECIPES\nDIET TIPS\nPODCASTS\nEat better.\nLose weight.\nGet healthy.\nFooducate empowers you to achieve your\ndiet, health, and fitness goals.\nDownload on the App Store Get it on Google Play\nI was never able to lose weight before. Thanks to Fooducate, I've lost 20 lbs in 6 months. An incredible, life changing app.\nJanice\nHealth Tracker\nTrack what you eat and your activities to see your progress and achieve your goals\nSTART TRACKING\nRecent Products\nBrowse Fooducate's extensive database to find the healthiest cereal, yogurt or snack for you\nArnold Bread, 100% Whole Wheat\nPB2 Peanut Butter With Premium Chocolate\nSkippy Peanut Butter, Natural, Creamy\nBROWSE PRODUCTS\nTrending Discussions\nHarness the power of Fooducate’s community to healthify your diet\nvegasgrl\nMade these Christmas tree ornaments this morning with my grandaughter 🥰 . I remember making ornaments with my grandmother and how special it was.  I would write my name as best as I could on the back and then she would write the year 🙂I still have them.                                     My grandaughter took her time and let each layer dry in between.                I felt anxious and let's rush!! .          Then I stopped and realized I am off today and I dont have to do cleaning or errands🥰. I soaked in the time with her and realized this is better than any meditation app today 💕 what are some of your special holiday memories?? whatever you celebrate ❤️✌️\n5 comments\n3 likes\n1 follower\nVIEW DISCUSSIONS\nDiet Tips\nQuick and easy reads to empower you on your diet journey. Brought to you from Fooducate’s staff\nFooducate\nDoes Your Body Need a Coffee Break?\nThe upcoming holidays are a great opportunity for a change of pace, to unwind and relax. For some of us, that's a really hard thing to do. Is coffee part of the problem?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n4 comments\n4 likes\nno followers\nVIEW DIET TIPS\nTrending Recipes\nCheck out great eats from fellow community members. Full nutrition info included!\nshelbsimone\nsautéed spinach\n5 minutes\nServes 1\n260 cal / srv\nno comments\nno likes\n1 follower\nVIEW RECIPES\nDownload on the App Store Get it on Google Play\nHome\nDiet Tips\nFAQ\nContact\nTerms of Service\nPrivacy Policy\n© Maple Media LLC, 2022 All rights reserved by Maple Media.\nAll marks, brands and names belong to the respective companies and manufacturers and are used solely to identify the companies and products.",
